title: 'The Great British Bake Off' Season 13, Episode 2: "Biscuit Week" | Everything Is Cake
description:
Kate and Amelia break down "Biscuit Week" from its puffed up macaron signature and bizarre Garibaldi biscuit technical to a stunning 3D biscuit mask showstopper.
Hosts: Kate Halliwell and Amelia Wedemeyer
Producer: Sasha Ashall
